OL,5,G2100 Inside the Ambulance
OL,6,     FIn a dramatic start to the new
OL,7,     Fseries, the West Midlands
OL,8,     FAmbulance Service treat a man who
OL,9,     Fstabbed a police dog, a woman with
OL,10,     Fa suspected stroke and a man on
OL,11,     Fhis fourth bout of pneumonia.
OL,12,G2200 Inside the Ambulance
OL,13,     FHard-working ambulance crews help
OL,14,     Fa shivering pensioner with
OL,15,     Fpossible sepsis, as well as a
OL,16,     Fsparky 95-year-old who's had a
OL,17,     Ffall.
