OL,5,G2300 The Disappearance of Shannon
OL,6,G     Matthews
OL,7,     FOn 19th February, 2008,
OL,8,     Fnine-year-old Shannon disappears
OL,9,     Fin West Yorkshire. Her mother is
OL,10,     Fdistraught and the community
OL,11,     Frallies in support, but no trace
OL,12,     Fcan be found.
OL,13,G0000 The Disappearance of Shannon
OL,14,G     Matthews
OL,15,     FWith increasing alarm sweeping
OL,16,     Fthrough Shannon's hometown and
OL,17,     FBritain at large, the search for
OL,18,     Fthe missing nine-year-old grows in
OL,19,     Fscale.
